info.title: Scryfall
info.description: Scryfall is a powerful Magic: The Gathering card search. Scryfall currently indexes official Magic cards that someone could obtain, collect, or feasibly build with for competitive or casual formats.

get.description: Retrieves a list of cards that match the search query.
Returns a Card based on a name search string.
Retrieves a list of up to 20 full English card names that could be autocompletions of the given string parameter.

post.description: Retrieves a list with the collection of requested cards.
